^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, first the bidding. I like Hope's 2D bid. There is a good chance of a diamond slam and that is a good way to start exploring. However, once Eddy  bids 2N, they can expect bad breaks, so Hope is content to play 3N. Over 2N, Kerrie has a couple of choices. I don't like 3D. I like either double, which suggests that she might want to penalize us or she could pass, and see what happens. It turns out I bid 3C, which Hope doubles, and we are in big trouble.|
