NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So, she has three hearts, three spades, two clubs, and a diamond at least. Therefore, she should definitely play the Jack of hearts and she definitely should not duck the heart, as she turned three heart tricks into two. The only trick in the hand is the entry problems. Hope has to unblock her spades and hearts. |
PG| ***** 29 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Once the Jack of hearts wins, she should play AK of spades, and A of hearts. Then she can play a diamond to the board, play her winning Queen of spades and King of hearts, and take her 2 club tricks for 9 tricks. The way she played it, if Eddy  figures out how to discard, she only takes 8 tricks. The trick on this hand is to count out your tricks at trick one, and play the cards in the right order to ensure 9 tricks. It is tricky but not difficult if you plan correctly and make sure you unblock.|
