^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let me discuss why Kerrie's 4H bid was excellent. Using Bergen count she has 19 Starting Points: 17 HCP, 1 length, and 1 quality suit. Once Eddy raises she can add 2 for the singleton and 1 for the 4 card side diamond suit. That gets her to 22 Bergen Points. Eddy should have six (or at least 5) to raise. So, partnership has at least 26 combined points and 4H is clear. |
