^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, mostly I want to discuss the auction because it is important to know how to bid after a takeout double. The most important bid is to redouble when you have 10 HCP. So, Hope should redouble for sure. By passing she is denying 10 HCP. If you have 10 points you usually redouble. Many also play Jordan 2N, where a 2N bid over the double shows a limit raise or better. In any case you may not pass over a takeout double with 10 or more points.|
